            <abstract>
                <p>Jesus healing the bleeding woman (or "woman with an issue of blood" and other variants) 
                    is one of the miracles of Jesus recorded in the synoptic gospels. The length of
                    the text transmitted as a protective prayer may vary (Mk 5:25–29 in <ref
                        type="mss" corresp="BMLacq756"/>
                    or Mk 5:25–34 in <ref type="mss" corresp="OMD002"/>)</p>
